    <h2 id="cordyceps-energy">How Cordyceps Mushroom Generates Real Cellular Energy</h2>

    <p>Among functional mushrooms, cordyceps (<em>Cordyceps militaris</em>) is the undisputed leader for energy enhancement. Unlike caffeine, which masks fatigue by blocking adenosine receptors, cordyceps increases the actual production of adenosine triphosphate (ATP) — the molecular energy currency that powers every cell in the human body. This fundamental difference means cordyceps energy builds over days and weeks, lasts throughout the day, and produces no crashes, jitters, or sleep disruption.</p>

